，不過炒嘅唔單止係我，而係成個部門十幾人，連上司嘅上司都俾人炒埋 。後尾先知原來係架船上面係載住一啲化學物品，擱淺之後洩漏到成個海都係，公司要負責處理污染物，一賠賠幾億。而事件裡面最無辜嘅係附近一個水清沙幼嘅太平洋小島，因為生態災害，要即時封鎖隔離。"},{"pid":"012c16ecf9bc864a6d6c1207845ab7e0c7c922d9","tid":2041023,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"其實又唔算好過份，只係去全公司最大的meeting room食飯(最多腦細係晒個層)，同事問我去邊度食，咪係meeting room囉，入面咁多位"},{"pid":"263c8f482c786e7754e5cec96d505b84cba183d4","tid":2041023,"uid":310593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"打完卡返左屋企，收工先再返黎打卡"},{"pid":"fc112e27f60911b50daf7cfada33d8ab62f92246","tid":2041023,"uid":265756,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"print 參考書，仲要彩色既。<br />\n同人妻同事扑野，佢仲要興奮到插到噴水...好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c606bfb309a65b95e98a27173d11b69fa16c8c","tid":2041023,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158957d280b28721ed176f0b866df65d1fd17f6b","tid":2041023,"uid":29497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"飲啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"我都試過帶咗枝vodka 返工，整返shot 先做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609894adc446e9842fcc6bfc67d95d002e595ea3","tid":2041023,"uid":1968,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"去隔離大廈見工<br />\n見左兩個鐘<br />\n返黎先知隔離老世打電話比我老細<br />\n最尾有offer"},{"pid":"ef6738b8655b161e12c1b6a131b614868794b0b7","tid":2041023,"uid":226785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d210e662c4bfbb810f22a7ea4939dcfd69768d97","tid":2041023,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:28:21.000Z","msg":"download AV片<br />\nPrint 書 (400 pages)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T16:23:58.000Z","msg":"有同事做過，結果辭職"},{"pid":"9ca9a3fe02f4e8e065131f591c5c7a2c37da32